ing: 2 (6 ounce) cans sliced black olives, drained
des: "A hefty Mexican-inspired dip like this will never last long at a party! Serve it with tortilla chips and stand back -- your guests are going to love it!"
ins: In a medium serving dish, mix the cream cheese, sour cream and green onions. Top with salsa, and layer with tomatoes, black olives and Cheddar cheese.
